and I didn't listen?

339
00:21:43,458 --> 00:21:44,479
Something like that?

340
00:21:45,482 --> 00:21:48,337
You have no idea how that ate
at me while you were gone.

341
00:21:48,588 --> 00:21:51,579
- I just kept thinking that was
the last  - You were right.

342
00:21:55,001 --> 00:22:00,423
You know, today,
seeing you with those people...

343
00:22:01,715 --> 00:22:03,452
It was like you had found yourself.

344
00:22:05,323 --> 00:22:07,676
