383
00:23:56,718 --> 00:23:59,322
You'll see a big sign pointing
to the way to Jericho, okay?

384
00:23:59,361 --> 00:24:00,576
Got it?

385
00:24:01,030 --> 00:24:02,930
Left, second right.

386
00:24:03,364 --> 00:24:04,695
Right, left,

387
00:24:04,734 --> 00:24:05,534
Right.

388
00:24:10,263 --> 00:24:11,671
Mimi, I...

389
00:24:11,902 --> 00:24:12,964
Don't worry.

390
00:24:13,658 --> 00:24:14,623
Don't worry.

391
00:24:14,873 --> 00:24:15,992
I'll be careful.

392
00:24:30,585 --> 00:24:31,974
<i>Here's what we're gonna do:</i>

393
00:24:31,975 --> 00:24:33,787
I know a place that's safe.

394
00:24:34,096 --> 00:24:36,411
We take Darcy and the kids
out of Jericho

395
00:24:36,507 --> 00:24:39,111
