420
00:25:52,283 --> 00:25:53,575
- Robert, wait.
- What?

421
00:25:55,929 --> 00:25:57,086
Let's think about this.

422
00:25:57,087 --> 00:25:58,919
What's the plan?
What are you going to do?

423
00:25:59,164 --> 00:26:02,675
You know, maybe the plan all
along was to get us out here.

424
00:26:03,601 --> 00:26:05,202
I gotta protect
my family, Sarah.

425
00:26:06,244 --> 00:26:07,575
And what about the package?

426
00:26:10,836 --> 00:26:12,369
It'll need to be moved.

427
00:26:27,881 --> 00:26:29,541
This isn't so bad, right?

428
00:26:29,590 --> 00:26:31,113
Hey, we've been
through worse.

429
00:26:31,156 --> 00:26:32,887
Remember the time we got stuck on
the roof of the...

430
00:26:32,888 --> 00:26:34,954
town hall in the middle
of a lightning storm, huh?

431
00:26:35,321 --> 00:26:37,250
We were so afraid the lightning
was going to...

