437
00:26:51,633 --> 00:26:52,887
Drink some water.

438
00:26:54,122 --> 00:26:55,164
It's frozen right through.

439
00:26:55,588 --> 00:26:56,534
What?

440
00:27:02,524 --> 00:27:05,591
