441
00:27:05,630 --> 00:27:06,807
You need to get inside.

442
00:27:08,273 --> 00:27:09,971
It'll hurt, but you can make it.

443
00:27:09,990 --> 00:27:11,707
- Jake, I'm staying.
- Listen to me!

444
00:27:12,406 --> 00:27:15,725
There's no point in both of us
freezing to death out there.

445
00:27:16,303 --> 00:27:18,329
- She's coming back.
- When?

446
00:27:19,661 --> 00:27:21,108
She's been gone for, like,
an hour.

447
00:27:21,109 --> 00:27:23,066
It'll take her a little while to
reach the patrol,

448
00:27:23,067 --> 00:27:24,725
but when she does,
she'll find someone.

449
00:27:24,726 --> 00:27:25,902
I know she'll find someone.

450
00:27:26,674 --> 00:27:28,391
