you need to go.

453
00:27:40,816 --> 00:27:43,247
You wouldn't leave me
any more than I'm leaving you.

454
00:27:46,585 --> 00:27:48,591
Mimi's strong.
She'll find her way.

455
00:28:01,190 --> 00:28:02,348
Wait...

456
00:28:02,349 --> 00:28:04,103
he said keep going east.

457
00:28:05,531 --> 00:28:07,132
No... southeast.

458
00:28:08,815 --> 00:28:12,210
And... look for a sign.

459
00:28:25,274 --> 00:28:27,203
Oh, God, I hate this place!

460
00:28:59,659 --> 00:29:00,778
Come on, man.

461
00:29:01,381 --> 00:29:02,442
You can't fall asleep.

462
00:29:02,538 --> 00:29:03,869
You got to stay up;
come on.

463
00:29:03,902 --> 00:29:05,195
You stopped shivering.
Come on.

464
00:29:05,196 --> 00:29:07,177
You got to talk to me--
come on, come on, buddy.

465
00:29:07,178 --> 00:29:08,480
You gotta talk to me.

466
00:29:08,519 --> 00:29:09,946
Talk to me, buddy.
Come on.

467
00:29:10,294 --> 00:29:11,491
I'm sorry.

468
00:29:11,586 --> 00:29:12,706
I'm really sorry.

469
00:29:12,707 --> 00:29:13,961
