00:29:20,595 --> 00:29:21,560
Doesn't matter.

474
00:29:21,561 --> 00:29:22,937
I was gonna call.

475
00:29:25,349 --> 00:29:26,409
I was gonna call.

476
00:29:26,410 --> 00:29:29,120
